originalText.text: The building itself is fine, but management is nonresponsive and unhelpful. There are mice, cockroaches, a frequently broken elevator, and other smaller maintenance requests that go unhandled. I personally had at least 5 mice and communicated this in person, via text, and through email several times before having the situation investigated further. Giving two stars because the neighbors are friendly and the location is great.
